head -n 5 /etc/passwd
root:x:0:0:root:/root:/bin/bash
bin:x:1:1:bin:/bin:/sbin/nologin
daemon:x:2:2:daemon:/sbin:/sbin/nologin
adm:x:3:4:adm:/var/adm:/sbin/nologin
lp:x:4:7:lp:/var/spool/lpd:/sbin/nologin
[sreejithr@localhost test_dir]$
[sreejithr@localhost test_dir]$ tail -n 5 /etc/passwd
tcpdump:x:72:72::/:/sbin/nologin
sreejithr:x:1000:1000:sreejithr:/home/sreejithr:/bin/bash
notes:x:1001:1001::/home/notes:/bin/bash
jenkins:x:1002:1002::/home/jenkins:/bin/bash
nginx:x:980:978:Nginx web server:/var/lib/nginx:/sbin/nologin
[sreejithr@localhost test_dir]$


3.Searching for Patterns
Use grep to find all lines containing the word "root" in /etc/passwd.
[sreejithr@localhost test_dir]$ grep "root" /etc/passwd
root:x:0:0:root:/root:/bin/bash
operator:x:11:0:operator:/root:/sbin/nologin
[sreejithr@localhost test_dir]$

4. Zipping and Unzipping
Compress the test_dir directory into a file named test_dir.zip using zip.
Unzip test_dir.zip into a new directory named unzipped_dir.

zip test_dir.zip test_dir
  adding: test_dir/ (stored 0%)
[sreejithr@localhost linuxcommandslearn]$ ls -l
total 4
lrwxrwxrwx. 1 sreejithr sreejithr  16 Nov 11 06:38 b.txt -> learningln/a.txt
drwxr-xr-x. 2 sreejithr sreejithr  32 Nov 11 06:29 learningln
lrwxrwxrwx. 1 sreejithr sreejithr  10 Nov 11 06:56 learninglndup -> learningln
drwxr-xr-x. 2 sreejithr sreejithr  33 Nov 11 15:09 test_dir
-rw-r--r--. 1 sreejithr sreejithr 168 Nov 11 19:54 test_dir.zip

unzip test_dir.zip -d unzipped_dir
Archive:  test_dir.zip
   creating: unzipped_dir/test_dir/
[sreejithr@localhost linuxcommandslearn]$

5. Downloading Files
Use wget to download a file from a URL (e.g., https://example.com/sample.txt).

[sreejithr@localhost linuxcommandslearn]$ wget https://www.gutenberg.org/files/1661/1661-0.txt
--2025-11-11 19:59:21--  https://www.gutenberg.org/files/1661/1661-0.txt
Resolving www.gutenberg.org (www.gutenberg.org)... 152.19.134.47, 2610:28:3090:3000:0:bad:cafe:47
Connecting to www.gutenberg.org (www.gutenberg.org)|152.19.134.47|:443... connected.
HTTP request sent, awaiting response... 200 OK
